{
  "title": "overview.md",
  "content": [
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "H1",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Your Writing, Liberated"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "The modern web is a trap. Bloated frameworks, paywalled tools, and endless busywork keep people dependent on an industry that profits from making websites harder than they should be."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "H2",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Create A Website With Just MarkDown Syntax!"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "This project is a different path. It doesn’t replace the whole web stack (yet), but it cuts straight through the nonsense:"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "if you can write in Markdown, you can publish a website."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "Right now, it’s a prototype. That means:"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "If you’re semi-tech-competent, you can already use it to turn writing into a site."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": [
        {
          "Plain": {
            "String": "If you’re a dev, you can help make it stronger, cleaner, and freer for everyone."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "indent": 0,
      "line_type": "Paragraph",
      "markdown": []
    },
